post.description:
Creates a phone call activity

**Create a phone call**

If assigning a regarding or any EntityReference attribute then ONLY assign Id and Logical name. NOTE: Activities are created as OPEN. The status can only be changed via a subsequent update.

```
{
  "regarding": {
    "Id": "fa77bc27-ed16-ea11-8121-000c29b3092e",
    "LogicalName": "upbeat_transaction"
  }
}
```

Updates a phone call activity

**Create a phone call**

If assigning a regarding or any EntityReference attribute then ONLY assign Id and Logical name

```
{
  "regarding": {
    "Id": "fa77bc27-ed16-ea11-8121-000c29b3092e",
    "LogicalName": "upbeat_transaction"
  },
  "uniqueid": "447adc58-1565-eb11-8196-000c29bfe7d3"
}
```

Adds or removes a member interest

**Associate a member interest**

The 'add' action must be used to associate an interest to a member using the Interest's GUID

```
{
  "comment_uniqueid": "The Primary Key GUID of the Member",
  "uniqueid": "e6b2b079-c8fa-e511-80d2-020050d00007",
  "interests": [
    {
      "comment_uniqueid": "The Primary Key GUID of the Interest",
      "uniqueid": "f4d62b3e-a4f3-e811-815f-000c29bfe7d3",
      "action": "add"
    }
  ]
}
```


**Disassociate a member interest**

The 'remove' action must be used to disassociate an interest to a member using the Interest's GUID

```
{
  "comment_uniqueid": "The Primary Key GUID of the Member",
  "uniqueid": "e6b2b079-c8fa-e511-80d2-020050d00007",
  "interests": [
    {
      "comment_uniqueid": "The Primary Key GUID of the Interest",
      "uniqueid": "f4d62b3e-a4f3-e811-815f-000c29bfe7d3",
      "action": "remove"
    }
  ]
}
```

